WEBVTT

00:02:00.421 --> 00:02:04.551
So when Rizwan buys heart medicine,

00:02:04.575 --> 00:02:07.845
he can key in these one-time passwords

00:02:07.869 --> 00:02:09.741
to a toll-free short code

00:02:09.765 --> 00:02:14.720
that we've set up on all
the telecom companies in Egypt

00:02:14.744 --> 00:02:16.239
for free.

00:02:16.263 --> 00:02:19.103
He gets a message --
call it the message of life --

00:02:19.913 --> 00:02:22.059
which reassures him

00:02:22.083 --> 00:02:27.373
that this medicine is not one of the 12
percent of all medicines in Egypt

00:02:28.599 --> 00:02:29.917
that are counterfeits.